bamtools
------------------------------------------
BamTools provides both a programmer's API and an end-user's toolkit for
handling BAM files.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.1-1
  libbamtools-devel-2.5.3-1bl1
  libbamtools2.5.3-2.5.3-1bl1
  libgcc1-12.4.0-3
  libjsoncpp-devel-1.9.6-1
  libjsoncpp26-1.9.6-1
  libstdc++6-12.4.0-3
  pkg-config-2.4.3-1
  zlib-devel-1.3.1-1
  zlib0-1.3.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.44-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-3
  libjsoncpp-devel-1.9.6-1
  ninja-1.12.1-1
  zlib-devel-1.3.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/pezmaster31/bamtools

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/pezmaster31/bamtools/archive/refs/tags/v2.5.3.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack bamtools-2.5.3-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./bamtools-2.5.3-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/bamtools-2.5.3-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/bamtools-2.5.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbamtools2.5.3-2.5.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbamtools-devel-2.5.3-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(bamtools)
  /usr/bin/bamtools.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/bamtools.README
  /usr/share/doc/bamtools/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/bamtools/README

(libbamtools2.5.3)
  /usr/bin/cygbamtools-2.5.3.dll

